### Layout & Styles

#### [NEW] [layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/amudh/Downloads/a2uidemo/website/src/app/layout.tsx)
Root layout with Inter font, dark theme, metadata.

#### [NEW] [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/amudh/Downloads/a2uidemo/website/src/app/globals.css)
Custom CSS variables for dark theme + red accent, smooth scrolling, gradient animations.

